I_z=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\int_{1/2}^{1}\frac{1}{u\sqrt{(1-u)}}e^{-z^2u}\,du=\sqrt{2}\int_{1/\sqrt{2}}^{1}\frac{1}{u\sqrt{1-u^2}}e^{-z^2u^2}\,du,
