I_z = \sqrt{2}\int_{\pi/4}^{\pi/2}\frac{\exp\left(-z^2\sin^2\theta\right)}{\sin\theta}\,d\theta=\sqrt{2}\int_{0}^{\pi/4}\frac{\exp\left(-z^2\cos^2\theta\right)}{\cos\theta}\,d\theta.\tag{1}
